{
  "page": "Bay of Seals",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_North.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The north and the location of the Bay of Seals\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of the Bay of Seals\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/400px-The_North.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"431\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/600px-The_North.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/The_North.png/800px-The_North.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 16.7%; left: 80.6%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 9px; font-size: 9px;\"><img alt=\"The north and the location of the Bay of Seals\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/9px-Wolff2.PNG\" title=\"Bay of Seals\" width=\"9\" height=\"9\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/14px-Wolff2.PNG 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ea/Wolff2.PNG/18px-Wolff2.PNG 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Bay of Seals</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> and the location of the Bay of Seals\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Bay of Seals</b> is a bay in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a> that extends from <a href=\"/index.php/Beyond_the_Wall\" title=\"Beyond the Wall\">beyond the Wall</a> to the shores that fall under the domain of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">House Umber</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> have a castle astride it, <a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-Sea</a>. Isles of the bay, which is named after the <a href=\"/index.php/Seal\" title=\"Seal\">animal</a>, include <a href=\"/index.php/Skagos\" title=\"Skagos\">Skagos</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Skane\" title=\"Skane\">Skane</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafbay_of_seals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafbay_of_seals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Geography\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Geography</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Geography\">Geography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Geography\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The grey and green waters of the Bay of Seals are choppy.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The wooded coastline to its south has rocks and whirlpools.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">Free folk</a> raiders sometime cross the Bay of Seals in small boats<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> and rafts.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos73.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">free folk</a> have crossed the Bay of Seals to raid the lands of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">House Umber</a> since the <a href=\"/index.php/Dawn_of_Days\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dawn of Days\">Dawn of Days</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd17.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In the <a href=\"/index.php/Feast_of_Skane\" title=\"Feast of Skane\">Feast of Skane</a>, stoneborn from <a href=\"/index.php/Skagos\" title=\"Skagos\">Skagos</a> raided <a href=\"/index.php/Skane\" title=\"Skane\">Skane</a>, allegedly rendering the isle uninhabited.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_stoneborn_of_skagos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_stoneborn_of_skagos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Brandon_IX_Stark\" title=\"Brandon IX Stark\">Brandon IX Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>, stopped Skagosi from raiding the mainland by destroying their ships and denying them the sea.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_stoneborn_of_skagos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_north:_the_stoneborn_of_skagos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Galleys from <a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-Sea</a> caught <i><a href=\"/index.php/Cobblecat\" title=\"Cobblecat\">Cobblecat</a></i> in the Bay of Seals.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Free_folk\" title=\"Free folk\">Free folk</a> in little boats cross the Bay of Seals and wash up on <a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">Umber</a> lands, causing <a href=\"/index.php/Hother_Umber\" title=\"Hother Umber\">Hother Umber</a> to demand that a fleet be built to stop the wildlings.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> sails from <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\">Eastwatch-by-the-Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Gilly\" title=\"Gilly\">Gilly</a>, and Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a> sail on <i><a href=\"/index.php/Blackbird\" title=\"Blackbird\">Blackbird</a></i> from Eastwatch across the Bay of Seals to <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When the fleet of <a href=\"/index.php/Salladhor_Saan\" title=\"Salladhor Saan\">Salladhor Saan</a> sails south from Eastwatch, <i><a href=\"/index.php/Oledo\" title=\"Oledo\">Oledo</a></i> and <i><a href=\"/index.php/Old_Mother%27s_Son\" title=\"Old Mother&#39;s Son\">Old Mother's Son</a></i> are driven onto <a href=\"/index.php/Skagos\" title=\"Skagos\">Skagos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd9.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>A savage storm rages on the Bay of Seals.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The Bay of Seals was a lot deeper than his waist, and not so friendly as that little fishpond below <a href=\"/index.php/Horn_Hill\" title=\"Horn Hill\">his father's castle</a>. Its waters were grey and green and choppy, and the wooded shore they followed was a snarl of rocks and whirlpools.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote> \n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>It was cold when the wind was blowing, but there was something bracing about the salt smell in the air.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Tarly\" title=\"Samwell Tarly\">Samwell Tarly</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bay_of_Seals&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafbay_of_seals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafbay_of_seals.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Bay of Seals.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Map_of_the_North\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Map of the North\">Map of the North</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">4.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\">4.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\">4.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\">4.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\">4.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc15.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\">4.5</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 15\">Chapter 15</a>, Samwell II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Sword